msgid "NARRATIVE_JOSEPHS_RISE_DESC"
msgstr "De l'esclavage à la puissance en Égypte"

msgid "NARRATIVE_JOSEPHS_RISE_MAIN"
msgstr "Joseph, vendu comme esclave, devint le vizir d'Égypte.\n\nIl sauva sa famille de la famine."

msgid "NARRATIVE_JOSEPHS_RISE_NAME"
msgstr "L'Ascension de Joseph"

msgid "NARRATIVE_JOSEPH_EXALTED_MAIN"
msgstr "Pharaoh made Joseph second-in-command\nover all of Egypt.\n\nFrom prisoner to prince in one day."

msgid "NARRATIVE_JOSEPH_FINAL_DAYS_MAIN"
msgstr "Joseph lived to see his great-grandchildren.\n\nBefore dying, he made them promise:\n'Carry my bones from this place.'"

msgid "NARRATIVE_JOSEPH_IMPRISONED_MAIN"
msgstr "Falsely accused, Joseph was thrown into prison.\n\nYet even there, the Lord was with him."

msgid "NARRATIVE_JOSEPH_INTERPRETS_DREAMS_MAIN"
msgstr ""

msgid "NARRATIVE_JOSEPH_INTERPRETS_MAIN"
msgstr ""

msgid "NARRATIVE_JOSEPH_REVEALED_MAIN"
msgstr "'I am Joseph, your brother,\nwhom you sold into Egypt.'\n\nTears and forgiveness followed."

msgid "NARRATIVE_JOSEPH_RISES_TO_POWER_MAIN"
msgstr ""

msgid "NARRATIVE_JOSEPH_SOLD_DESC"
msgstr "Trahi par ses frères"

msgid "NARRATIVE_JOSEPH_SOLD_MAIN"
msgstr "Joseph's brothers sold him to traders\nand told their father he was dead.\n\nBetrayal by blood."

msgid "NARRATIVE_JOSEPH_SOLD_NAME"
msgstr "Joseph vendu comme esclave"

msgid "NARRATIVE_LAST_SUPPER_MAIN"
msgstr ""

msgid "NARRATIVE_LET_MY_PEOPLE_GO_MAIN"
msgstr "Moses and Aaron stood before Pharaoh:\n\n'Thus says the Lord:\nLet My people go!'"

msgid "NARRATIVE_LIFE_OF_JESUS_MAIN"
msgstr ""

msgid "NARRATIVE_MANNA_QUAIL_MAIN"
msgstr ""

msgid "NARRATIVE_MERIBAH_WATER_MAIN"
msgstr ""

msgid "NARRATIVE_MIDWIVES_COURAGE_MAIN"
msgstr "Pharaon ordonna la mise à mort des garçons hébreux,\nmais les sages-femmes craignirent Dieu\net laissèrent les enfants vivre."

msgid "NARRATIVE_MIRACLES_IN_EGYPT_MAIN"
msgstr ""

msgid "NARRATIVE_MOSES_ADOPTED_MAIN"
msgstr "Pharaoh's daughter raised Moses\nas her own son.\n\nA Hebrew prince in Egypt's palace."

msgid "NARRATIVE_MOSES_BIRTH_DESC"
msgstr "La naissance miraculeuse de Moïse"

msgid "NARRATIVE_MOSES_BIRTH_MAIN"
msgstr "Moïse naquit d'une famille hébraïque en Égypte.\n\nPour échapper à la mort, il fut placé dans un panier sur le Nil."

msgid "NARRATIVE_MOSES_BIRTH_NAME"
msgstr "La Naissance de Moïse"

msgid "NARRATIVE_MOSES_BORN_MAIN"
msgstr ""

msgid "NARRATIVE_MOSES_CALLING_DESC"
msgstr "L'appel divin de Moïse"

msgid "NARRATIVE_MOSES_CALLING_MAIN"
msgstr "Dieu appela Moïse depuis un buisson ardent.\n\nIl reçut la mission de libérer les Israélites de l'esclavage."

msgid "NARRATIVE_MOSES_CALLING_NAME"
msgstr "L'Appel de Moïse"

msgid "NARRATIVE_MOSES_FLEES_DESC"
msgstr "Moïse s'enfuit en Madian"

msgid "NARRATIVE_MOSES_FLEES_MAIN"
msgstr "Après avoir tué un Égyptien, Moïse s'enfuit pour échapper à la colère de Pharaon.\n\nIl trouva refuge chez Jéthro, un prêtre de Madian."

msgid "NARRATIVE_MOSES_FLEES_NAME"
msgstr "La Fuite de Moïse"

msgid "NARRATIVE_MOSES_FLEES_TO_MIDIAN_MAIN"
msgstr ""

msgid "NARRATIVE_MOSES_IN_BASKET_MAIN"
msgstr "A mother placed her baby in a basket\nand set him in the Nile.\n\nPharaoh's daughter found him."

msgid "NARRATIVE_MOSES_RETURNS_TO_EGYPT_MAIN"
msgstr ""

msgid "NARRATIVE_MOUNT_SINAI_MAIN"
msgstr ""

msgid "NARRATIVE_NEW_HEAVENS_NEW_EARTH_MAIN"
msgstr ""

msgid "NARRATIVE_NEW_PHARAOH_MAIN"
msgstr "A new king arose over Egypt,\nwho did not know Joseph.\n\nHe feared the Israelites' numbers."

msgid "NARRATIVE_NOAH_CALLED_MAIN"
msgstr "God saw the wickedness of mankind\nand decided to flood the earth.\n\nBut Noah found favor in God's eyes."

