msgid "NARRATIVE_PLAGUES_CONTINUE_DESC"
msgstr "La puissance de Dieu se manifeste"

msgid "NARRATIVE_PLAGUES_CONTINUE_MAIN"
msgstr "Gnats, flies, and pestilence\nstruck the land of Egypt.\n\nYet Pharaoh would not relent."

msgid "NARRATIVE_PLAGUES_CONTINUE_NAME"
msgstr "Les Fléaux Continuent"

msgid "NARRATIVE_PLAGUES_DESC"
msgstr "Les fléaux d'Égypte"

msgid "NARRATIVE_PLAGUES_LIVESTOCK_BOILS_MAIN"
msgstr "The livestock died,\nand painful boils broke out on all Egyptians.\n\nThe plagues grew worse."

msgid "NARRATIVE_PLAGUES_NAME"
msgstr "Les Dix Plaies"

msgid "NARRATIVE_PLAGUES_SUMMARY_MAIN"
msgstr ""

msgid "NARRATIVE_PLAGUE_BLOOD_MAIN"
msgstr "Aaron struck the Nile with his staff,\nand all the water turned to blood.\n\nBut Pharaoh's heart was hardened."

msgid "NARRATIVE_PLAGUE_DARKNESS_MAIN"
msgstr "Darkness covered Egypt for three days,\nso thick it could be felt.\n\nBut Israel had light in their dwellings."

msgid "NARRATIVE_PLAGUE_FIRSTBORN_MAIN"
msgstr ""

msgid "NARRATIVE_PLAGUE_FROGS_DESC"
msgstr "La deuxième plaie"

msgid "NARRATIVE_PLAGUE_FROGS_MAIN"
msgstr "Frogs covered the land of Egypt,\nin houses, bedrooms, and ovens.\n\nStill Pharaoh refused."

msgid "NARRATIVE_PLAGUE_FROGS_NAME"
msgstr "La Plaie des Grenouilles"

msgid "NARRATIVE_PLAGUE_HAIL_DESC"
msgstr "Destruction venant du ciel"

msgid "NARRATIVE_PLAGUE_HAIL_MAIN"
msgstr "Hail and fire rained from the sky,\ndestroying crops and killing cattle.\n\nEgypt had never seen such devastation."

msgid "NARRATIVE_PLAGUE_HAIL_NAME"
msgstr "La Plaie de la Grêle"

msgid "NARRATIVE_PLAGUE_LOCUSTS_DESC"
msgstr "Le nuage dévastateur"

msgid "NARRATIVE_PLAGUE_LOCUSTS_MAIN"
msgstr "Locusts covered the ground\nuntil the land was black.\n\nThey devoured everything the hail had left."

msgid "NARRATIVE_PLAGUE_LOCUSTS_NAME"
msgstr "La Plaie des Sauterelles"

msgid "NARRATIVE_PRISON_DREAMS_DESC"
msgstr "Joseph interprète des rêves"

msgid "NARRATIVE_PRISON_DREAMS_MAIN"
msgstr "Joseph interpreted the dreams\nof Pharaoh's cupbearer and baker.\n\nEverything happened as he said."

msgid "NARRATIVE_PRISON_DREAMS_NAME"
msgstr "Rêves en Prison"

msgid "NARRATIVE_QUEEN_OF_SHEBA_MAIN"
msgstr ""

msgid "NARRATIVE_RACHEL_AT_WELL_DESC"
msgstr "Jacób rencontre sa bien-aimée"

msgid "NARRATIVE_RACHEL_AT_WELL_MAIN"
msgstr "Jacob met Rachel at a well\nand fell in love immediately.\n\nHe would work fourteen years to marry her."

msgid "NARRATIVE_RACHEL_AT_WELL_NAME"
msgstr "Rachel au puits"

msgid "NARRATIVE_RAINBOW_COVENANT_MAIN"
msgstr "God placed a rainbow in the sky\nas a sign of His promise:\n\n'Never again will I flood the earth.'"

msgid "NARRATIVE_REBEKAH_AT_WELL_DESC"
msgstr "Une épouse pour Isaac"

msgid "NARRATIVE_REBEKAH_AT_WELL_MAIN"
msgstr "Abraham's servant prayed for a sign,\nand Rebekah appeared at the well.\n\nShe would become Isaac's wife."

msgid "NARRATIVE_REBEKAH_AT_WELL_NAME"
msgstr "Rébecca au puits"

