msgstr ""

msgid "NARRATIVE_THREE_VISITORS_MAIN"
msgstr "Three mysterious visitors came to Abraham.\n\nThey promised that Sarah would bear a son,\ndespite her old age."

msgid "NARRATIVE_TOWER_OF_BABEL_MAIN"
msgstr "Mankind tried to build a tower to heaven.\n\nGod confused their language\nand scattered them across the earth."

msgid "NARRATIVE_TWELVE_TRIBES_MAIN"
msgstr "Jacob had twelve sons,\nwho would become the twelve tribes of Israel.\n\nGod's promise was multiplying."

